<div class="content-page">
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

  <h2>How LighterMe Earns Money</h2>
  <p>LighterMe is an affiliate website. This means we earn a commission when you click one of our affiliate links, visit a clinic's website, and sign up for a programme.</p>

  <p>Here's how it works:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>You click an affiliate link on our site</li>
    <li>A tracking cookie is set by the affiliate network (usually Awin)</li>
    <li>If you sign up for a programme within the cookie duration (typically 30 days), we earn a referral fee</li>
    <li>The commission is paid to us by the clinic/network — not by you</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>You never pay more</strong> — our commission does not increase the price you pay for any programme</li>
    <li><strong>We don't handle your money</strong> — all payments go directly to the clinic</li>
    <li><strong>We don't access your health data</strong> — we only know that a referral was made, not your medical information</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Editorial Independence</h2>
  <p>Our content and recommendations are based on independent research. We commit to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Only listing clinics we have independently verified</li>
    <li>Never recommending a programme solely because it pays a higher commission</li>
    <li>Being transparent about our affiliate relationships</li>
    <li>Clearly labelling affiliate links on our site</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Programmes We Work With</h2>
  <p>We currently have affiliate relationships with programmes available through the Awin affiliate network, including clinician-led weight management providers verified on our <a href="/compare">comparison page</a>.</p>

  <h2>Compliance</h2>
  <p>This disclosure is made in compliance with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The Consumer Protection from Unfair Trading Regulations 2008</li>
    <li>The Advertising Standards Authority (ASA) CAP Code</li>
    <li>The Competition and Markets Authority (CMA) guidelines on online endorsements</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about our affiliate relationships, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@lighterme.co.uk">hello@lighterme.co.uk</a>.</p>
</div>

